# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Both .env and .env.local are gitignored.
# This file is for the LINEAR hooks only.
#
# Linear is OPTIONAL — the only value you may need here is your personal Linear API key.
# Without it, the Linear hooks skip cleanly. Shared non-secret team/state IDs are
# already committed in .claude/linear.shared.env — do NOT duplicate them here.
#
# The GitHub MCP token does NOT go here: GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN is a
# Claude Code / OS environment variable (set via `setx` or ~/.claude/settings.local.json
# "env"), read by .mcp.json — not by this file.
#
# Personal Linear API key — create at: https://linear.app/settings/api
LINEAR_API_KEY=lin_api_...
